Or rain here?

114
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:53,060
Don't forget.

115
00:09:53,349 --> 00:09:55,309
The magnetic field here
is totally messed up.

116
00:09:56,100 --> 00:09:57,498
Those people who passed by...

117
