135
00:10:42,860 --> 00:10:43,600
Let's go.

136
00:11:22,077 --> 00:11:23,077
What the heck is this place?

137
00:11:26,902 --> 00:11:28,842
After a long day of effort,

138
00:11:29,429 --> 00:11:31,409
