160
00:13:10,513 --> 00:13:11,057
Left.

161
00:13:12,914 --> 00:13:14,028
Right.

162
00:13:17,034 --> 00:13:18,054
How do you know?

163
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:19,900
I...

164
00:13:23,291 --> 00:13:24,191
