246
00:19:39,940 --> 00:19:41,460
Old man, enough!

247
00:19:41,760 --> 00:19:42,663
If you keep bawling,
I'll dump you here!

248
00:19:42,900 --> 00:19:43,600
Go back on your own!

249
00:19:51,483 --> 00:19:52,023
Wu Xie,

250
00:19:52,420 --> 00:19:53,743
