277
00:21:49,360 --> 00:21:49,928
True.

278
00:21:50,240 --> 00:21:52,440
It scared me to death.

279
00:21:53,711 --> 00:21:54,771
Such a huge rat,

280
00:21:54,771 --> 00:21:56,691
